{"title":"devicePixelRatio","uid":"6b187a3dcaca4b22050a31027cd39624","slug":"devicePixelRatio","date":"2023-07-07T17:03:01.920Z","updated":"2023-07-07T17:03:43.563Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/devicePixelRatio.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>#HTML</p>\n<h1 id=\"概述\"><a href=\"#概述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"概述\"></a>概述</h1><p> <strong><code>devicePixelRatio</code></strong> 返回当前显示设备的 <em><strong>物理像素分辨率与 CSS 像素分辨率之比。</strong></em> 此值也可以解释为像素大小的比率：一个 CSS 像素的大小与一个物理像素的大小。简单来说，它告诉浏览器应使用多少屏幕实际像素来绘制单个 CSS 像素。</p>\n<h1 id=\"语法\"><a href=\"#语法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"语法\"></a>语法</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>devicePixelRatio<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h1 id=\"值\"><a href=\"#值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"值\"></a>值</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path s